  "short_description": "Embrace your inner jeepney driver once again in the big, bustling streets of Manella City! Pick up passengers, calculate change, and weave through traffic in this one-of-a-kind driving game. Bring your friends, customize your jeepneys, and face rising quotas. Will you survive? or fade into history?",
