  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CAREER MODE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/fe2cbf6f4cea6669582ff32ef6ca749b.poster.avif?t=1732797532\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/fe2cbf6f4cea6669582ff32ef6ca749b.webm?t=1732797532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/fe2cbf6f4cea6669582ff32ef6ca749b.mp4?t=1732797532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Do you think you have what it takes to be a pro jeepney driver? Test your skills in Jeepney Simulator 2's <strong>CAREER MODE!</strong> Race against the clock as you hone your driving skills, memorize routes, and upgrade your jeepney to keep up with the ever-increasing boundary. Remember: Every peso counts! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FREERIDE MODE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/538ed7b64f3986c49b2940979dac3e4a.poster.avif?t=1732797532\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/538ed7b64f3986c49b2940979dac3e4a.webm?t=1732797532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/538ed7b64f3986c49b2940979dac3e4a.mp4?t=1732797532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>FREERIDE MODE</strong> is a way for players to experience Jeepney Simulator 2 in a stress-free way. Customize the game to your heart's content and do away with the challenge of the boundary. It's very useful for learning the basics and memorizing the streets of Manella City. Prepare to kick back and relax with your favorite playlist!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURING THE BIG, BUSTLING MANELLA CITY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/36c323e7ea547bab5ea44df043ad8f84.poster.avif?t=1732797532\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/36c323e7ea547bab5ea44df043ad8f84.webm?t=1732797532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/36c323e7ea547bab5ea44df043ad8f84.mp4?t=1732797532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Immerse yourself in a city based on the real thing! With familiar landmarks as <i>Tondoo</i>, <i>Rizz El Park</i>, and <i>BBC</i>, you'll feel right at home. And with the addition of a few unique landmarks, we guarantee there's lots of adventure to be had!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>POLICE CHASES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/065886f1abaee122dd3461421ee9c01c.poster.avif?t=1732797532\" width=800 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/065886f1abaee122dd3461421ee9c01c.webm?t=1732797532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/065886f1abaee122dd3461421ee9c01c.mp4?t=1732797532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make sure you obey the law because Manella's Finest are now in action! <i><u>Avoid running red lights, unloading illegally, and hitting cars and pedestrians</u></i> or else you will be chased by whatever Manella Police have at their disposal. They have cruisers, SUVs, and even APCs! But when caught, players have the option to either <strong>pay the fines</strong>, <strong>go to jail</strong>, or <strong>bribe the officer</strong>. Even in Manella City, cash is king.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>REALISTIC DRIVING AND IMMERSIVE GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/687410d656362542afa1ab2ff36b537c.poster.avif?t=1732797532\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/687410d656362542afa1ab2ff36b537c.webm?t=1732797532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/687410d656362542afa1ab2ff36b537c.mp4?t=1732797532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>REALISTIC GRAPHICS</strong> and <strong>VEHICLE PHYSICS</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rotating steering wheel and moving gear shift, with <strong>INVERSE KINEMATICS</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HEAR THE JEEPNEY ROAR</strong> with immersive audio </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple, yet <strong>REALISTIC DRIVING</strong>! Watch your RPM meter and change gears at the right time!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the arrow keys to activate the <strong>turn indicators</strong>. They actually work!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>REALISTIC TRAFFIC SYSTEM</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/9613d073016596db3b6a08468cabc133.poster.avif?t=1732797532\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/9613d073016596db3b6a08468cabc133.webm?t=1732797532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/9613d073016596db3b6a08468cabc133.mp4?t=1732797532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Navigate the busy streets and weave through traffic! Stop at traffic lights, wait for pedestrians, and keep an eye on the road!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>OTHER FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FULL VEHICLE CUSTOMIZATION</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ROAD EVENTS AND ACCIDENTS</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BUYABLE HOMES</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GAS STATIONS</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TOW TRUCKS</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >COMMUNITY-UPLOADED VOICE LINES!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A COMPLETE MANELLA CITY</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>See you on the road, drivers!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/b16b8e28543711cb91f82cb566c559e9.poster.avif?t=1732797532\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/b16b8e28543711cb91f82cb566c559e9.webm?t=1732797532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819970/extras/b16b8e28543711cb91f82cb566c559e9.mp4?t=1732797532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
